      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You can use what you know about an incoming spell to increase your defenses against it.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Int 13 or Wis 13</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Once every 10 minutes, when you successfully identify a spell—as it is being cast—with a @Check[type:mysticism], the split-second warning at what’s coming gives you +1 circumstance bonus on any saving throw you make against that spell. If you can cast the identified spell, increase the bonus to +2.</p>"
